1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,140
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:47,180 --> 00:00:48,780
=Episode 19=
=Wedding with No Bride=

11
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,120
Niannian.

12
00:01:07,350 --> 00:01:08,280
What are you doing?

13
00:01:12,710 --> 00:01:13,550
Does it hurt?

14
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,510
Ready to tell me now

15
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:20,790
what Xiaodi's death

16
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,710
had to do with your mother?

17
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:27,510
In this world, I trust only two people.

18
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,040
One is you.

19
00:01:31,350 --> 00:01:32,840
The other is my mother.

20
00:01:34,070 --> 00:01:36,350
If someone has to take responsibility
for Xiaodi's death,

21
00:01:38,430 --> 00:01:39,590
it should be me.

22
00:01:50,710 --> 00:01:52,040
As long as you're happy,

23
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,040
whatever you do,

24
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:57,000
I'm okay with it.

25
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,750
I'm giving you one last chance.

26
00:02:19,630 --> 00:02:20,470
I saw

27
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,560
you enter Ye Mei's gallery.

28
00:02:25,030 --> 00:02:26,080
What exactly do you

29
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,710
and your mother
have to do with Xiaodi's death?

30
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,240
Niannian.

31
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,280
Seems like there were

32
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,960
petals on your lashes.

33
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:39,470
Very beautiful.

34
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:44,840
Just like the night we first met.

35
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,630
In your hair,

36
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,000
there were petals too.

37
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:58,840
And I thought

38
00:03:00,590 --> 00:03:02,630
if only you'd hold me like that forever.

39
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,080
Shut up!

40
00:03:05,150 --> 00:03:06,710
We'll be happy.

41
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:10,430
Niannian.

42
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:12,910
Trust me.

43
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:16,460
I'll make sure
you're happy every single day.

44
00:03:27,430 --> 00:03:28,270
Why?

45
00:03:29,900 --> 00:03:31,190
I'm even treating you like this.

46
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:33,430
Why?

47
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:38,270
Because...

48
00:03:41,250 --> 00:03:42,130
I love you.

49
00:03:42,150 --> 00:03:46,220
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

50
00:03:46,500 --> 00:03:50,210
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

51
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:54,740
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

52
00:03:55,710 --> 00:03:56,870
From beginning to end,

53
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,710
I only have you.

54
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:38,960
Does your hand

55
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:41,710
still hurt?

56
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,560
You can hate me.

57
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:55,310
How could I ever?

58
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,400
Don't touch me.

59
00:05:14,510 --> 00:05:15,350
I'm dirty.

60
00:05:33,980 --> 00:05:34,700
(Organ Trafficking)

61
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:36,220
(Heart, Fresh Donor, O RH-Negative)

62
00:05:38,540 --> 00:05:41,180
(Organ Trafficking)

63
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:42,360
What's the owner's name?

64
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:45,600
A very famous artist, Ye Mei.

65
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:52,830
What am I supposed to do?

66
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,760
Ye Lang.

67
00:05:56,190 --> 00:05:57,630
Is this your love

68
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,310
or your scheme?

69
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:23,380
(Typing Test Report)

70
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:25,660
(Ye Lang, Jiang Xiaodi)

71
00:06:29,510 --> 00:06:30,350
No way.

72
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:32,030
Ye Lang.

73
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:33,790
Xiaodi.

74
00:06:36,950 --> 00:06:37,790
No way.

75
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,160
The blood bank got units here in time.

76
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,310
Luckily you arrived in time.

77
00:06:42,950 --> 00:06:44,600
Being a match for him is incredibly rare.

78
00:06:45,660 --> 00:06:46,560
The surgery went well.

79
00:06:51,180 --> 00:06:54,220
(Ye Lang)

80
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:58,030
Sorry,

81
00:06:58,310 --> 00:07:00,480
the subscriber you dialed is power off.

82
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,320
Sorry,

83
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:04,570
the subscriber you dialed is power off.

84
00:07:05,110 --> 00:07:06,070
Sorry,

85
00:07:06,250 --> 00:07:08,420
the subscriber you dialed is power off.

86
00:07:08,420 --> 00:07:09,310
Sorry,

87
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:12,320
the subscriber you dialed is power off.

88
00:07:18,050 --> 00:07:18,900
Alright.

89
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,510
Go check the area around.

90
00:07:23,750 --> 00:07:24,800
What's wrong, Ms. Jiang?

91
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:26,870
You agreed to a full exam now?

92
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:28,150
Dr. Zheng,

93
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,120
is Ye Lang with you?

94
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,510
He's not answering his phone.

95
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:32,120
He and I

96
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,390
would only meet in the morgue.

97
00:07:33,970 --> 00:07:34,820
What?

98
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:36,600
Wanna join us?

99
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:43,120
Then this morgue

100
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,510
is quite unique.

101
00:07:45,830 --> 00:07:46,670
Zheng Lu.

102
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,000
Love-brain,

103
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,390
your Ms. Jiang is coming.

104
00:07:52,190 --> 00:07:53,190
You think I'd buy that?

105
00:07:53,580 --> 00:07:54,830
It's just rehearsal these days.

106
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,040
Let her cool off first.

107
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,800
I'll surprise her later.

108
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,400
I can't stand a fool.

109
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:01,590
Bye.

110
00:08:04,070 --> 00:08:04,910
Niannian.

111
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,600
Let's go, guys. Good work today.

112
00:08:10,870 --> 00:08:11,800
What are you doing here?

113
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,720
I came to see

114
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:17,190
what you've been hiding from me.

115
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:19,600
This is the gallery you found

116
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,720
under my mother's name.

117
00:08:22,430 --> 00:08:24,750
It's also the old house
where my mother and I lived.

118
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,480
I grew up here.

119
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,800
This is where you grew up?

120
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,440
That's right.

121
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:35,240
Later, my mom made it an art gallery.

122
00:08:36,700 --> 00:08:38,440
I've been preparing everything day and night,

123
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,910
just to give you a perfect proposal.

124
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:45,510
(This is his home,)

125
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:48,840
(and also the source of that dark web IP.)

126
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:50,550
(What's going on?)

127
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:08,840
I won't give you a chance to throw it away.

128
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,840
I want to be your forever home,

129
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,560
your safe place

130
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,240
when you're tired.

131
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:35,920
Niannian.

132
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:37,600
I didn't expect

133
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:39,990
you'd say yes.

134
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,480
Only by staying with you

135
00:09:47,870 --> 00:09:49,000
can I finally see clearly

136
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,630
what you're really after.

137
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:01,120
Ye Lang proposed to me.

138
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:03,750
We're getting married in three days.

139
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,560
From now on,

140
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:07,000
we'll be one family.

141
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,040
Congratulations.

142
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,600
I hope

143
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,270
you'll be my bridesmaid.

144
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:16,260
Of course.

145
00:10:16,270 --> 00:10:17,110
My honor.

146
00:10:19,670 --> 00:10:20,510
By the way,

147
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:23,120
how's Li Hong doing lately?

148
00:10:24,860 --> 00:10:25,980
He's still in the sanatorium,

149
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,600
refusing to see anyone.

150
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,150
He hasn't been doing well.

151
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:36,080
Actually, I have a favor to ask.

152
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:39,550
I hope Li Hong can attend our wedding.

153
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,800
Don't worry.

154
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,840
I'll let him know.

155
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:44,720
Li Hong told me

156
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,080
he didn't blame Ye Lang.

157
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:47,590
Ye Lang

158
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,390
is always his brother.

159
00:10:50,270 --> 00:10:51,110
That's great.

160
00:10:52,270 --> 00:10:53,200
I'll get going then.

161
00:10:53,550 --> 00:10:55,440
There's so much to do for the wedding.

162
00:10:55,450 --> 00:10:56,290
Go ahead.

163
00:10:56,390 --> 00:10:58,840
The most beautiful bride in the world.

164
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:16,870
Why did you agree?

165
00:11:17,910 --> 00:11:18,750
Li Hong.

166
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:21,630
Stop ruining Ye Lang and Niannian's joy.

167
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,790
Why do you care so much about Ye Lang?

168
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,440
What about me?

169
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,870
Why did I end up with nothing?

170
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:31,270
Ye Lang has won over the board.

171
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,390
Everything is settled.

172
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:34,920
Hong.

173
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,270
Stop this.

174
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,360
Ye Lang

175
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:43,510
took everything that should've been mine.

176
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:46,350
Hong.

177
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,390
That's how the world works.

178
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,200
The winner

179
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,080
takes all.

180
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:53,240
You're no match for him.

181
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:54,870
Stop now.

182
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,870
Living an ordinary life isn't so bad.

183
00:12:11,670 --> 00:12:12,510
Xue.

184
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:15,120
I'll make everyone see

185
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:17,240
who deserves to stand at the top.

186
00:12:18,910 --> 00:12:20,910
Ye Lang and Jiang Niannian,

187
00:12:21,790 --> 00:12:25,150
I'll make sure they rot unburied.

188
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:44,840
Why are you here?

189
00:12:46,790 --> 00:12:47,960
Didn't you invite me?

190
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:01,030
What do you want?

191
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:03,960
I

192
00:13:04,670 --> 00:13:06,150
want to take you somewhere.

193
00:13:33,090 --> 00:13:39,650
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

194
00:13:41,490 --> 00:13:47,690
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

195
00:13:48,250 --> 00:13:55,250
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

196
00:13:55,970 --> 00:13:58,450
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

197
00:13:58,450 --> 00:14:03,450
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

198
00:14:03,450 --> 00:14:07,690
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

199
00:14:08,210 --> 00:14:12,130
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

200
00:14:12,170 --> 00:14:15,970
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

201
00:14:15,970 --> 00:14:21,730
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

202
00:14:21,730 --> 00:14:26,050
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

203
00:14:26,090 --> 00:14:29,890
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

204
00:14:29,890 --> 00:14:34,410
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

205
00:14:34,410 --> 00:14:39,250
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

206
00:14:39,650 --> 00:14:46,210
♪Life finds its way again♪
